videos.description: Thon Maker takes a slick pass from Larry Nance Jr. and rises to the rim for a powerful slam in the Cavaliers' preseason game vs. the Pacers.

videos.description: Cavaliers rookie Isaac Okoro scores 18 points on the night, 16 of which came in the fourth quarter, to power Cleveland to a 107-104 preseason win over Indiana.
